3. What is a Russian manicure, and why is it popular?
A Russian manicure involves using an electric file to meticulously clean and shape the nails, resulting in impeccable precision and long-lasting results. This technique is popular because it offers a clean, polished look and lasts longer than traditional manicures. Code Hair's skilled technicians provide the best Russian manicure in Dubai.
